data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Tenant had to cancel at the last minute. Beautiful home in desirable Woods at Oakmont. 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Plenty of Natural Light! The kitchen is open to the family room, granite counter tops and plenty of storage. Enjoy the cover patio and so much more! This house will be ready for a great tenant on June 1st!
